Welcome to Elite Medical Wellness

Here at Elite Medical Wellness Center, we believe that weight loss can be achieved naturally.

That means our programs come with:

No hunger
No injections
No medications
No long hours in the gym

Just sustainable, real wellness, when your body operates how it was meant to.

We understand that there is no one-size-fits-all diet. That’s why we have enlisted the help of modern technology to better assess your current state of health and evaluate your body’s unique needs. Knowing the key factors contributing to your weight gain will give us the necessary insights to provide you with a plan that works for YOU.”

Take Charge of your health

Step 1

Assess

Because the body is constantly changing, our Non-invasive Metabolic Report and ZOE Foodmap Scan looks at your health as a whole. We analyze your body’s current state of health, and identify your body’s unique and current needs from day one.

Step 2

Plan

Based on your Elite Medical Foodmap, our health coaches will show you what common foods are helping -or harming- your progress, and map out a targeted weight loss program for you. Eat real, delicious meals created to reset your metabolism and help you thrive.

FAQ

How do I know Elite Medical is right for me? 

We, at Elite Medical , recognize that each and every body works differently. That is why our initial consultation process is one of the most important steps! We pinpoint and identify what your body is telling you and we guide you on what your body will be thanking you!

What does Elite Medical , how are we different than other programs? What else can Elite Medical help with that other programs cannot?

We use bioelectric impedance technology that provides body composition analysis to accurately assess each individual. We also use frequency resonance technology to allow a deeper look into the person’s biology in order to tailor more to the individual.

 

Secondly, our program not only helps with fat loss but the possibility of reducing the dosage of your medication, or better yet, getting Completely off medication by raising food intake awareness. This heightened awareness positively changes ones eating behaviors, etc.

 

Thirdly, you gain the knowledge through working with our health coaches. You learn how to portion out foods so one doesn’t overindulge often. It is important to plan ahead, knowing and understanding your eating schedule.

What does BCA mean?

BCA stands for body composition analysis. This will give you a detailed analysis of factors including total weight, body mass index, body fat percentage, total body percentage, visceral fat, and metabolic age.

Is exercise a requirement to lose weight during the Elite Medical Wellness program?

Exercise is not required during the Elite Medical program. We actually encourage clients to avoid exercise but to stay physically active but means of moving their bodies through walking, riding their bike, gardening, washing cars, etc.

What if I have more questions?

Don’t worry at all! If you have more questions, please feel free to contact us at 770-637-2928 or email us at support@zoewellness.com
